%N A396310 a(n)/9! is the coefficient of x^9 in the Taylor expansion of the k-th iteration of sin(x).
%C A396310 See A366834 for more information.
%H A396310 Jianing Song, <a href="/A396310/b396310.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..10000</a>
%H A396310 <a href="/index/Rec#order_05">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, signature (5,-10,10,-5,1).
%F A396310 a(n) = binomial(n,1) + 1870*binomial(n,2) + 20244*binomial(n,3) + 29400*binomial(n,4) = 1225*n^4 - 3976*n^3 + 4288*n^2 - 1536*n.
%F A396310 G.f.: x/(1-x)^2 + 1870*x^2/(1-x)^3 + 20244*x^3/(1-x)^4 + 29400*x^4/(1-x)^5.
%F A396310 E.g.f.: exp(x)*x*(1 + 935*x + 3374*x^2 + 1225*x^3).
%e A396310 sin(sin(x)) = x - 2*x^3/3! + 12*x^5/5! - 128*x^7/7! + 1872*x^9/9! - ...;
%e A396310 sin(sin(sin(x))) = x - 3*x^3/3! + 33*x^5/5! - 731*x^7/7! + 25857*x^9/9! - ...;
%e A396310 sin(sin(sin(sin(x)))) = x - 4*x^3/3! + 64*x^5/5! - 2160*x^7/7! + 121600*x^9/9! - ....
%o A396310 (PARI) a(n) = 1225*n^4 - 3976*n^3 + 4288*n^2 - 1536*n
%Y A396310 Cf. A051624 (coefficient of x^5), A366827 (coefficient of x^7).
